    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game &quot;Vulpestale&quot; you have to take on the role of a wandering fox who embarks on a journey through a mysterious forest. Fascinating puzzles and riddles await you, which will require you to show your resourcefulness and ingenuity to overcome them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The forest is full of ancient mechanisms such as sliding gates, levers, switches and pressure plates. Along the way, you will also encounter altars that need to be activated correctly or find the right key.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/3517252650008a12dcb99d4971c4620e.poster.avif?t=1766698558\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/3517252650008a12dcb99d4971c4620e.webm?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/3517252650008a12dcb99d4971c4620e.mp4?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, you can find items in the game that will help you customize the appearance of your character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/756c3786f9b9c2aa96b74bd0956957a7.poster.avif?t=1766698558\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/756c3786f9b9c2aa96b74bd0956957a7.webm?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/756c3786f9b9c2aa96b74bd0956957a7.mp4?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a calm and peaceful atmosphere that helps the player to relax and fully immerse themselves in the gameplay. Solve fascinating puzzles and unravel the secrets of this amazing forest.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/66b3bb5826feabfab1c8270637061d38.poster.avif?t=1766698558\" width=616 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/66b3bb5826feabfab1c8270637061d38.webm?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122700/extras/66b3bb5826feabfab1c8270637061d38.mp4?t=1766698558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
